pageProduct.name: Plunkett's Vita E Pure Vitamin E Oil 25ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Super concentrated pure Vitamin E Oil enriched with Rosehip Oil. For use on dry patches, wrinkles and scars or as a booster to your moisturiser. For use on face, hands and body.

Plunkett's VIta E Oil is a super concentrated pure Vitamin E Oil enriched with Rosehip Oil. This high potency (910 IU per gram) oil uses Natural Vitamin E which is more potent than synthetic vitamin E and makes is easier to absorb. This oil protects and nourishes against moisture loss, dehydration and the signs of ageing. Ideal for scars, dry patches or as a beauty booster.

Suitable For: Suitable for softening scars, using as a beauty booster with your moisturiser, and for small dry, damaged patches

Size: 25mL

KEY FEATURES

• The drop by drop applicator makes dispensing the oil easy.
• Vitamin E: helps skin retain natural moisture and eases dryness while antioxidants neutralise damaging free radicals generated by the environment. Softens and smoothes skin by replenishing moisure.
• Rosehip Oil: is rich in Vitamin A & C and essential fatty acids (Omega 3 & 6), helping to improve skin elasticity and suppleness.

Warnings

For external use only. Store below 30°C

Ingredients

Tocopheryl Acetate 910 IU/gram (Vitamin E), Rosa Canina Fruit Oil (Rosehip Oil), Benzyl Alcohol. Does not contain mineral oil, parabens or frragrance

Active Ingredients: Natural Vitamin E (910 IU per gram)
Rosehip Oil

Directions

Apply to the affected area, massaging gently into skin twice a day or as needed. Can be used on face, hands and body
